    <item>
      <title>税收变化导致银行持有的市政债券跌至九年来的最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/bank-holdings-of-muni-debt-fall-to-nine-year-low-on-tax-changes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于应税市政证券的销售额下降且贷款机构继续享受较低企业税率的好处，美国银行对州和地方债务的投资处于近九年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/bank-holdings-of-muni-debt-fall-to-nine-year-low-on-tax-changes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 15:31:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
